@page "/"

<PageTitle>PolyMyMarket - Prediction Markets</PageTitle>

<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row align-items-center mb-5">
        <div class="col-lg-6">
            <h1 class="display-3 fw-bold mb-4">
                Trade on the Future
            </h1>
            <p class="lead mb-4">
                PolyMyMarket is a prediction market platform where you can bet on the outcomes of real-world events. 
                Buy shares in Yes or No outcomes, and profit when you're right.
            </p>
            <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-md-flex">
                <a href="/markets" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg px-4 me-md-2">
                    Browse Markets
                </a>
                <a href="/portfolio" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg px-4">
                    My Portfolio
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 text-center">
            <div class="display-1 mb-3">🎯📈💰</div>
            <h3 class="text-muted">Bet on What You Believe</h3>
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="my-5" />

    <div class="row g-4 mb-5">
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
                    <div class="display-4 mb-3">📊</div>
                    <h4 class="card-title">Real-Time Prices</h4>
                    <p class="card-text text-muted">
                        Market prices adjust automatically based on supply and demand using an automated market maker.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
                    <div class="display-4 mb-3">💸</div>
                    <h4 class="card-title">Low Fees</h4>
                    <p class="card-text text-muted">
                        Trade with minimal costs. Buy and sell shares instantly with transparent pricing and no hidden fees.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
                    <div class="display-4 mb-3">🏆</div>
                    <h4 class="card-title">Earn Rewards</h4>
                    <p class="card-text text-muted">
                        When markets resolve, winning shares pay out $1.00 each. The more accurate your predictions, the more you earn.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
            <div class="card border-primary">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <h4 class="card-title mb-3">How It Works</h4>
                    <ol class="lead">
                        <li class="mb-3">
                            <strong>Browse Markets:</strong> Explore prediction markets on various topics from crypto to politics.
                        </li>
                        <li class="mb-3">
                            <strong>Buy Shares:</strong> Purchase Yes or No shares based on your prediction. Prices reflect the crowd's confidence.
                        </li>
                        <li class="mb-3">
                            <strong>Trade Anytime:</strong> Buy and sell shares before markets close. Prices fluctuate as new information emerges.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Get Paid:</strong> When markets resolve, winning shares are worth $1.00 each. Losing shares become worthless.
                        </li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-5">
        <h3 class="mb-4">Ready to Start Trading?</h3>
        <a href="/markets" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg px-5">
            View All Markets
        </a>
    </div>
</div>
